A2UI (Agent to UI) Protocol

Thank you for your interest in A2UI! A new open source UI Toolkit to facilitate LLM-generated UIs. A2UI is built with A2A and allows an A2A server agent to send interactive components instead of just text, using a high level framework-agnostic format that can be rendered natively on any surface (web, mobile).

We will be sharing more soon. Sign up here to learn when we publish more details about A2UI.
